      <title>波兰启动 2025 年外汇债券发售，以填补创纪录的融资计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/poland-starts-2025-fx-debt-sales-to-fill-record-funding-needs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰即将启动今年首次外币债券发售，旨在满足创纪录的融资需求，并加入美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普上任前新兴市场债券发行热潮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/poland-starts-2025-fx-debt-sales-to-fill-record-funding-needs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 11:07:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
